# Generated visualization renders. They embed the vendored Mermaid runtime
# (~2.5 MB each for Mermaid-format views), and any developer re-running the
# viz pipeline against the worked example would otherwise accumulate them.
# The committed `visuals/tree.md` is the canonical lightweight reference.
*/docs/product/visuals/*.html
*/docs/product/visuals/.snapshots/

# Generated read-once Export docs (timestamped + content-hashed). Export is a
# read-once consume surface — no curated example export is committed.
*/docs/product/exports/
